---
import Layout from '../components/layout/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms and conditions for using VStorage"
>
  <div class="py-4xl bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-lg md:px-xl">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-h1 md:text-display text-gray-900 mb-lg">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-body-lg text-gray-700 mb-lg">
          <strong>Effective Date:</strong> January 15, 2025
        </p>
        <p class="text-body text-gray-700 italic border-l-4 border-primary pl-lg py-md bg-primary-tint">
          This document is provided for informational purposes. While we strive for accuracy, this does not constitute legal advice. For legal questions, consult a qualified attorney.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">1.1 Agreement</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-md">
            By accessing or using VStorage ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you don't agree to these Terms, please don't use the Service.
          </p>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-xl">
            VStorage is intended for commercial use by professional musicians, producers, studios, and labels.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">1.2 Eligibility</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>You must be 18 years or older, or have parental consent</li>
            <li>You must have authority to enter into contracts</li>
            <li>You must comply with all applicable laws</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">1.3 Account Registration</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>You must provide accurate information</li>
            <li>One account per email address</li>
            <li>You're responsible for account security</li>
            <li>Notify us immediately of unauthorized access: security@vstorage.ch</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">2. Service Description</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">2.1 The Service</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-md">VStorage provides:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Cloud storage for lossless audio files</li>
            <li>Supported formats: WAV, FLAC, Apple Lossless (ALAC), AIFF</li>
            <li>Zero-knowledge encrypted storage</li>
            <li>Swiss data residency</li>
            <li>Features as described on vstorage.ch</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">2.2 Service Levels</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>99.9% uptime target</li>
            <li>Excludes scheduled maintenance (announced in advance)</li>
            <li>Service credits available for extended downtime</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">2.3 Service Modifications</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>We may modify features with notice</li>
            <li>Material changes: 30 days advance notice</li>
            <li>You may terminate your account if you disagree with changes</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">3. Acceptable Use Policy</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">3.1 Permitted Use</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Lawful storage of your audio files</li>
            <li>Professional music production</li>
            <li>Archival of recordings</li>
            <li>Collaboration with authorized users</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">3.2 Prohibited Use</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-md">You may NOT use VStorage for:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Illegal content (pirated music, illegal recordings)</li>
            <li>Copyrighted material without proper rights</li>
            <li>Malware, viruses, or harmful code</li>
            <li>Content that violates others' rights</li>
            <li>Spam or bulk unsolicited content</li>
            <li>Automated abuse or excessive API use</li>
            <li>Circumventing security measures</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">3.3 Consequences of Violations</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>Warning for first violation</li>
            <li>Suspension for repeated violations</li>
            <li>Termination for serious violations</li>
            <li>Legal action if warranted</li>
            <li>No refunds for terminated accounts</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 4 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">4. Your Content and Data</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">4.1 Ownership</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>You own all files you upload</li>
            <li>You retain all rights to your content</li>
            <li>We claim no ownership of your music</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">4.2 License to Us</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-md">
            You grant us a limited license to store and transmit your files, <strong>only</strong> to provide the Service. Due to zero-knowledge encryption, we cannot access your content. This license terminates when you delete files.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">4.3 Your Responsibility</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>You're responsible for content legality</li>
            <li>You must have necessary rights to upload</li>
            <li>You're responsible for maintaining your own backups</li>
            <li>We provide redundancy but recommend local backups</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">4.4 Copyright Infringement</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>We respect copyright (Swiss Copyright Act)</li>
            <li>Report infringement: dmca@vstorage.ch</li>
            <li>We will investigate valid claims</li>
            <li>Repeat infringers will be terminated</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 5 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">5. Privacy and Security</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">5.1 Privacy</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for details</li>
            <li>Zero-knowledge architecture</li>
            <li>We cannot access your files</li>
            <li>Swiss privacy law applies</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">5.2 Security</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>AES-256-GCM encryption</li>
            <li>You're responsible for password security</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication (recommended)</li>
            <li><strong>Lost password = lost data</strong> (we cannot recover)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">5.3 Data Breach Notification</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We will notify you within 72 hours of any data breach. Note: Due to zero-knowledge encryption, encrypted data is not useful to attackers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 6 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">6. Payments and Billing</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">6.1 Pricing</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Custom pricing based on your needs</li>
            <li>Contact us for quote: contact@vstorage.ch</li>
            <li>Prices in CHF (Swiss Francs) or USD</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">6.2 Payment Terms</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Monthly or annual billing available</li>
            <li>Payment due in advance</li>
            <li>Credit card and bank transfer options available</li>
            <li>Subscription management with easy cancellation</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">6.3 Refunds</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>30-day satisfaction guarantee for new accounts</li>
            <li>Flexible cancellation terms for annual plans</li>
            <li>No refunds for violations of these Terms</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">6.4 Late Payment</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Account suspended after 7 days overdue</li>
            <li>Account terminated after 30 days overdue</li>
            <li>Data deleted 30 days after termination</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">6.5 Price Changes</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>60 days notice for price increases</li>
            <li>Grandfathered pricing for annual plans</li>
            <li>You may cancel before increase takes effect</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 7 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">7. Account Termination</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">7.1 Termination By You</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Cancel anytime from account settings</li>
            <li>Data held for 30-day recovery period</li>
            <li>No refunds for mid-month cancellation</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">7.2 Termination By Us</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>For violations of these Terms</li>
            <li>For non-payment</li>
            <li>For illegal activity</li>
            <li>30 days notice (except for serious violations)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">7.3 Data Upon Termination</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>30-day grace period to download files</li>
            <li>Permanent deletion after 30 days</li>
            <li>No recovery after permanent deletion</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 8 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">8. Service Availability</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">8.1 Uptime Commitment</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Designed for 99.9% uptime availability target</li>
            <li>Scheduled maintenance excluded</li>
            <li>Advance notice for planned downtime</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">8.2 Downtime Credits</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Service credits framework planned for future production use</li>
            <li>Must request credit within 30 days</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">8.3 Force Majeure</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We are not liable for events beyond our reasonable control (natural disasters, war, government action, etc.).
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 9 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">9. Limitations of Liability</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">9.1 Service "As Is"</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Service provided without warranties</li>
            <li>No guarantee of fitness for particular purpose</li>
            <li>No guarantee of error-free operation</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">9.2 Liability Limitation</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Our liability limited to fees paid in past 12 months</li>
            <li>No liability for indirect or consequential damages</li>
            <li>No liability for lost profits or data loss</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">9.3 Data Loss</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>We provide redundancy but you should maintain backups</li>
            <li>Not liable for data loss (except gross negligence)</li>
            <li>Zero-knowledge means we cannot recover lost passwords</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">9.4 User Responsibility</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>You're responsible for your account security</li>
            <li>You're responsible for content legality</li>
            <li>You're responsible for maintaining backups</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 10 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">10. Indemnification</h2>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-md">
            You agree to indemnify and hold VStorage harmless from any claims, damages, or expenses arising from:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>Your use of the Service</li>
            <li>Your content or files</li>
            <li>Your violation of these Terms</li>
            <li>Your violation of any law or third-party rights</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 11 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">11. Intellectual Property</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">11.1 Our Intellectual Property</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>VStorage name, logo, and website are our property</li>
            <li>Service design and features are our property</li>
            <li>You may not copy, imitate, or misuse our IP</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">11.2 Your Intellectual Property</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>You retain all rights to your files</li>
            <li>We claim no IP rights to your content</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 12 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">12. Dispute Resolution</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">12.1 Governing Law</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Swiss law applies</li>
            <li>Jurisdiction: Zürich, Switzerland</li>
            <li>Swiss data protection principles guide our operations</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">12.2 Arbitration</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>Disputes may be resolved by arbitration (optional)</li>
            <li>Swiss Rules of International Arbitration</li>
            <li>Venue: Zürich, Switzerland</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">12.3 Class Action Waiver</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            No class actions permitted. All claims must be brought individually.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 13 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">13. General Provisions</h2>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md mt-xl">13.1 Entire Agreement</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-xl">
            These Terms, together with our Privacy Policy, constitute the complete agreement and supersede all prior agreements.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">13.2 Severability</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-xl">
            If any provision is invalid, the remaining provisions remain in effect.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">13.3 No Waiver</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-xl">
            Our failure to enforce any provision doesn't waive our right to enforce it later.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">13.4 Assignment</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700 mb-xl">
            <li>You cannot assign your account to another party</li>
            <li>We may assign (e.g., in case of corporate acquisition)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-md">13.5 Notices</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-xl space-y-sm text-body text-gray-700">
            <li>Send legal notices to: legal@vstorage.ch</li>
            <li>We'll use your account email for notices</li>
            <li>Terms updates posted on website</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 14 -->
        <section class="mb-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-h2 text-gray-900 mb-lg">14. Contact</h2>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-xl rounded-card">
            <p class="text-body text-gray-700 mb-lg"><strong>Questions about these Terms:</strong> legal@vstorage.ch</p>

            <p class="text-body text-gray-700 mb-sm"><strong>Mail:</strong></p>
            <p class="text-body text-gray-700 mb-sm">VStorage</p>
            <p class="text-body text-gray-700">Zürich, Switzerland</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="mt-4xl pt-xl border-t border-gray-300 text-center">
          <p class="text-body text-gray-700">
            <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 15, 2025
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
